Package: wspaces
Type: Package
Title: Build and mnipulate word spaces (a.k.a. word embedding models).
Version: 0.1.0
Author: J. T. Atria
Maintainer: J. T. Atria <jtatria@gmail.com>
Description: wspaces packages a number of useful functions for distributional semantic modelling,
    a set of interface functions for a Lucene index      backend and a set of fuctions to enforce
    some reasonable conventions for lexical datasets and the necessary file formats to store and
    read them.
License: GPL v3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.11),
    RcppParallel,
    Matrix,
    magrittr,
    data.table,
    rJava,
    igraph
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppEigen,
    RcppParallel
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
SystemRequirements: Java, GNU make
